						               													<description>Mezcla2 proposes solving challenges in groups of 2 or 3 people. It consists of a deck of cards with images of characters that make different mimics and another with slogans / challenges. Each player must meet with those who have the same card and solve the slogan. The judge will decide which group wins and scores points. Then all the cards will be shuffled to start a new game with a new group and judge. This game proposes slogans that will never be solved in the same way because they depend on each group.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mezcla2 is an invitation to meet others, get to know each other and take action to solve as a team.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A game that promotes cooperation, group work and adaptation.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
